adultAltar.hintText: An awakening voice from the Sacred&Realm will call those destined to be&Sages, who dwell in the five temples.^$8Forest Temple...^$3Spirit Temple...^$4Link's Pocket...^$5Shadow Temple...^$6Dodongo's Cavern...^$7Fire Temple...^$lThe awakened ones will await&for the Hero to find %gGreg%w.^$bAnd the %revil one%w's key will be&provided by Zelda once %r5&Spiritual Stones and Medallions%w&are retrieved.^$kTogether with the Hero of Time,&the awakened ones will return&the light of peace to the world...

ganonText: Today, let's begin down&'The Hero is Defeated' timeline.
ganonHintText: Ha ha ha... You'll never beat me&by reflecting my lightning bolts&and unleashing the arrows from&%rDesert Colossus%w!^And even if you do, you'll never&find the legendary blade hidden in&%rthe Graveyard%w!

dampeText: Whoever reads this, please enter&%rLake Hylia%w. I will let you&have my stretching, shrinking&keepsake.^I'm waiting for you.&--Dampé
